OL,5,BSubmitting longer articles             
OL,7,BThe edit server primarily gets used for
OL,8,Eteletext art,Bbut Chunkytext is about  
OL,9,Bmore than that.                        
OL,11,BIf you'd like to write a longer article
OL,12,Babout yourEhobby, Youtube channel, fish
OL,13,Emotorcycling academy, etc.Bcontact:    
OL,15,Bchunkytext@zxnet.co.uk or @ZXGuesser   
OL,17,FNo teletext editing ability necessary. 
